txt.en: '[placeholder]! I have new orders for you! Scout-master Ausma requests your aid in the Pit of Stonejaws, the hobgoblin seat of power! Please proceed to Bárgstad as soon as you are able!'
To the Pit of Stonejaws DNT NOT USED
'Good to see you, [placeholder]! I'm glad my runner was able to find you. I have my hands full here, and welcome your competency!'
Ausma has requested your aid in her mission in the Pit of Stonejaws.\n\nYou will find Scout-master Ausma at the dwarf-camp Bárgstad.
A runner from Scout-master Ausma has found you. Your orders are to assist her and her scouts in the Pit of Stonejaws.
